quran[13]{c,v,t}:
  49,1,"Ko onon yo Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e ! wata on adito yeeso Allah e NulaaЙ—o Makko on. Hulee Allah. Pellet, Allah ko Nanoowo, Yi'oowo"
  49,2,"Ko onon yo Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e ! wata on towu sowtooji mon e hoore sowto Annabaajo on, wata on ewnor mo kadi konngol, wano no yoga mon ewnorta yoga, sakko golle mon Й—en bonata, hara on so'aa-anndude"
  49,3,"Pellet, Й“en joltinooЙ“e sowtooji maЙ“Й“e Й—in ka NulaaЙ—o Allah on, ko Й“en woni Й“e Alla jarabii Й“erЙ—e mun Й—en gomЙ—al. Hino woodani Й“e haforanal e njoЙ“di mawndi"
  49,4,"Pellet, Й“en Й“e no noddire ka Й“aawo cuuЙ—i, ko Й“uri Й—uuЙ—ude e maЙ“Й“e, wanaa haqqilooЙ“e"
  49,5,"Sinno Й“e muГұГұino haa yaltaa e maЙ“Й“e, ko Й—um Й“uraynoo moЖҙЖҙannde Й“e. Allah ko Haforoowo, HinnotooЙ—o"
  49,6,"Ko onon yo Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e ! Si faasiqiijo ardanii on e kumpital, tefee fii wata on heЙ“or e yimЙ“e sabu majjeede, wonton ninsuЙ“e e kon ko waЙ—uЙ—on"
  49,7,"Anndee wonnde NulaaЙ—o Allah on hino hakkunde mon. Si o tewtino on e ko Й—uuЙ—i e fiyakuuji, on tampayno. Kono Allah yiЙ—ini on gomЙ—inal, O cuЙ—ini ngal e Й“erЙ—e mon; O aГұini on keeferaaku, e faasiqaaku e geddi. Ko Й“en woni feewuЙ“e Й“en"
  49,8,"Й—um ko Й“ural immorde ka Allah e neema. Allah ko AnnduЙ—o, Г‘eeГұuЙ—o"
  49,9,"Si feddeeji Й—iЙ—i e gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en haЙ“ii, moЖҙЖҙintinee hakkunde maЙ“Й“e. Si fedde goo bewii e hoore ndeya, ko haЙ“ugol wonnde e bewude nden, haa nde ruttoo e yamiroore Allah nden. Si nde ruttike, moЖҙЖҙintiniree hakkunde maЙ“Й“e nunЙ—al. NunЙ—ee, tawde pellet, Allah no yiЙ—i nunЙ—ooЙ“e Й“en"
  49,10,"Anndee gomЙ—imЙ“e Й“en ko jeyduЙ“e. Haray moЖҙЖҙinee hakkunde jeydal mon ngal, hulon Allah, belajo'o on yurminte"
  49,11,"Ko onon yo Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e ! Wata yimЙ“e jalnor yimЙ“e : hino gasa hara Й“en (jalaaЙ“e) hino Й“uri Й“e moЖҙЖҙude. Wanaa rewЙ“e woni ko jalnorta rewЙ“e : hino gasa hara Й“en no Й“uri Й“e moЖҙЖҙude. Wata on aybidnir ko'e-mon, wata on bugondir jammooje (bonЙ—e). Innde faasiqaaku nden bonii Й“aawo nde gomЙ—inal nden. Kala mo tuubaali, ko Й“en woni tooГұuЙ“e Й“en"
  49,12,"Ko onon yo Й“en gomЙ—imЙ“e ! WoЙ—Й—itee e ko Й—uuЙ—i e sikke. Pellet, yoga e sikke ko bakkaatu. Wata on wiЙ—ondir, wata yoga mon Гұo'u yoga. Hara gooto e mo'on yiЙ—ay Гұaamugol teewu musiЙ—Й—o mun maayЙ—o? HiЙ—on aГұi Й—um. Hulee Allah. Pellet, Allah ko JaЙ“oowo tuubuubuyee, HinnotooЙ—o"
  49,13,"Ko onon yo yimЙ“e ! Men tagiriii on immorde e gorel e deyel, Men waЙ—iri on leЖҙЖҙi e gori, fii yo on anndindir. Pellet, Й“urЙ“e teddude e mon Й“en ka Allah, ko Й“urЙ“e gomЙ—ude Й“en e mon. Pellet, Allah ko AnnduЙ—o, HumpitiiЙ—o"